642
01:01:28,560 --> 01:01:30,490
Ne!

643
01:01:30,700 --> 01:01:32,220
Ne!

644
01:01:41,450 --> 01:01:43,670
Jste v pořádku, pane?

645
01:01:46,950 --> 01:01:50,900
